Package: ai-z
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: ocl-icd-libopencl1, libvulkan1
Suggests: clinfo, vulkan-tools
Description: TUI performance timelines and benchmarks (CPU/GPU/Disk/PCIe)
 ai-z is a terminal UI (TUI) app that displays performance timelines and runs
 quick benchmarks. OpenCL/Vulkan benchmarks are built in by default, but remain
 runtime-optional via dynamic loading.
